          "text1637": "[q] Ende een van sijne Discipelen [29] was aensittende inden schoot Iesu, [30] welcken Iesus lief hadde.",
          "text1637_html": "<sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"q\">q</sup> Ende een van sijne Discipelen <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"29\">29</sup> was aensittende inden schoot Iesu, <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"30\">30</sup> welcken Iesus lief hadde.",
          "marginNotes": [
