          "ref": "bibjoha013:25",
          "text1637": "Ende dese [31] vallende op de borst Iesu, seyde tot hem, Heere, wie is't?",
          "text1637_html": "Ende dese <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"31\">31</sup> vallende op de borst Iesu, seyde tot hem, Heere, wie is't?",
          "marginNotes": [
