        {
          "number": 27,
          "ref": "bibjoha013:27",
          "text1637": "Ende [33] na de bete, [34] doe voer de Satan in hem. Iesus dan seyde tot hem, Dat ghy [35] doet, doet het haestelick.",
          "text1637_html": "Ende <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"33\">33</sup> na de bete, <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"34\">34</sup> doe voer de Satan in hem. Iesus dan seyde tot hem, Dat ghy <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"35\">35</sup> doet, doet het haestelick.",
          "marginNotes": [
            {
