        {
          "number": 19,
          "ref": "bibjoha014:19",
          "text1637": "Noch eenen kleynen [tijdt], ende de werelt [40] en sal my niet meer sien: maer [41] ghy sult my sien: want ick [42] leve, ende [43] ghy sult leven.",
          "text1637_html": "Noch eenen kleynen [<i>tijdt</i>], ende de werelt <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"40\">40</sup> en sal my niet meer sien: maer <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"41\">41</sup> ghy sult my sien: want ick <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"42\">42</sup> leve, ende <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"43\">43</sup> ghy sult leven.",
          "marginNotes": [
            {
              "marker": "40",
              "type": "explanatory",
              "text1637": "Gr. en siet my niet meer."
