          "text1637": "Ende nu [13] verheerlickt my ghy Vader by u selven, met de heerlickheyt, [f] die ick by u hadde, [14] eer de werelt was.",
          "text1637_html": "Ende nu <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"13\">13</sup> verheerlickt my ghy Vader by u selven, met de heerlickheyt, <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"f\">f</sup> die ick by u hadde, <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"14\">14</sup> eer de werelt was.",
          "marginNotes": [
