          "text1637": "Dit opschrift dan lasen vele van de Ioden: want de plaetse, daer Iesus gecruyst wiert, was na by de stadt: ende het was geschreven in't Hebreeusch, in't Grieksch, [ende] [36] in't Latijn.",
          "text1637_html": "Dit opschrift dan lasen vele van de Ioden: want de plaetse, daer Iesus gecruyst wiert, was na by de stadt: ende het was geschreven in't Hebreeusch, in't Grieksch, [<i>ende</i>] <sup class=\"note-marker\" data-note=\"36\">36</sup> in't Latijn.",
